Description: This is the madison design briefcase, made of black croc-print, jacquard fabric and smooth black leather. It is accented with striking contrast stitching. It features silver and black designer zipper pulls and the brighton hanging heart is present on the double shoulder handles. Also included long adjustable shoulder or cross-body strap.  This lovely bag is a large tote measuring 14 3/4" Wide at the base, 16" across the top, 11" tall and 4 1/2" deep and has a number of pockets to keep you organized.  The interior is divided into 3 large main interior sections - one of which has a keychain leash. The exterior of the bag has six front pockets and 1 outside back pocket. 9" handles, 21" detachable strap.  Brand new, with the inspection tag still inside. Please note.
